starvationevasion.sim

Class State

  • java.lang.Object
    • starvationevasion.sim.State

  • public class State
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by Alfred on 11/15/15. The State class describes a state in the United States.
    Each is classified by region, total land, total farm land, and
    components to calculate how much land is dedicated to a specific
    piece of agriculture.
